    <string name="terms_text">TERMS OF USE\n\n1. End-User License: We grant you a personal, non-transferable, and limited license to play Enigma Bottles.\n2. Economy: In-game items (coins, lives, skins) hold no real monetary value.\n3. Content adjustments: We reserve the right to regulate challenge reward policies at any time.\n4. IP: All artwork, custom shaders, symbols, and concepts are protected intellectual property.</string>
    <string name="privacy_text">PRIVACY POLICY\n\n1. Data Collection: We gather anonymous game metrics (playtime, logical moves) to optimize layout parameters.\n2. Local Space: Your database and cosmetic unlocks reside entirely inside local device SQLite cache.\n3. Ads Networks: Third party advertisers (AdMob) may retrieve device advertising identifiers.\n4. Opt-Out: Erasing app storage cache purges all locally stored profile metadata.</string>
